Resource Profile: FrPractitionerAgregateur

Official URL: https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/sas/StructureDefinition/sas-practitioner-aggregator Version: 1.1.0
Active as of 2025-01-31 Computable Name: FrPractitionerAgregateur

Profil de Practitioner, dérivé de FrPractitioner, pour le service d’agrégation de créneaux de la plateforme SAS - Commun cas d’usage PS Indiv et CPTS

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: BundleAgregateur and BundleAgregateurCPTS
  • Refer to this Resource Profile: FrPractitionerRoleExerciceAgregateur
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Practitioner/ExamplePractitioner, Practitioner/ExamplePractitioner2 and Practitioner/ExamplePractitioner3
